<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>New Paid Reservation - Driver Assignment</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #47B2E4 0%, #293751 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #47B2E4 0%, #293751 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -50%;
      left: -50%;
      width: 200%;
      height: 200%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
      animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .header img {
      max-width:200px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      height:100px;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.5; }
      50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.8; }
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .welcome-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: #293751;
    }

    .welcome-section p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #333;
    }

    .status-badge {
      background: #47B2E4;
      color: white;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      font-weight: 600;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .reservation-details h3,
    .followup-section h3,
    .footer h3 {
      color: #293751;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #47B2E4;
    }

    .details-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .detail-card {
      background: #f4f8fc;
      border: 1px solid #d3e9f8;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .detail-card strong {
      display: block;
      color: #293751;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .detail-card span {
      color: #47B2E4;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .followup-section {
      background: #e9f6fd;
      border-left: 5px solid #47B2E4;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .followup-section p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .footer {
      background: #f0f4f9;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      border-top: 1px solid #d0e2f2;
    }

    .footer p {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #47B2E4;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .payment-confirmation {
      background: #e8f5e9;
      border-left: 5px solid #4caf50;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .payment-confirmation h3 {
      color: #2e7d32;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .important-note {
      background: #fff8e1;
      border-left: 5px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        margin: 10px;
        border-radius: 15px;
      }

      .header {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }

      .header h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .details-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container" role="main">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="https://aspirebridgerwanda.org/abyride-logo.png" alt="Abyride Logo" />
      <h1>ðŸ’° Paid Reservation Assigned</h1>
      <p>Client has already paid - please proceed with pickup</p>
    </div>

    <section class="content welcome-section" aria-label="Welcome message">
      <h2>Hello {{driverName}},</h2>
      <p>You've been assigned a <strong>pre-paid</strong> reservation. The client has already completed payment.</p>
      
      <div class="payment-confirmation">
        <h3>âœ… Payment Confirmed</h3>
        <p>This reservation is fully paid. Your earnings will be processed after successful trip completion.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content reservation-details" aria-label="Reservation details">
      <h3>Client & Trip Details</h3>
      <div class="details-grid">
        <div class="detail-card">
          <strong>Client Name</strong>
          <span>{{clientName}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-card">
          <strong>Client Phone</strong>
          <span>{{clientPhone}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-card">
          <strong>Client Email</strong>
          <span>{{clientEmail}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-card">
          <strong>Pickup Location</strong>
          <span>{{pickup}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-card">
          <strong>Dropoff Location</strong>
          <span>{{dropoff}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-card">
          <strong>Scheduled Time</strong>
          <span>{{scheduledDateTime}}</span>
        </div>
        {{!-- <div class="detail-card">
          <strong>Passengers</strong>
          <span>{{passengers}}</span>
        </div> --}}
        <div class="detail-card">
          <strong>Reservation Number</strong>
          <span>{{reservationNumber}}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

   
    <section class="content followup-section" style="margin:35px" aria-label="Next steps">
      <h3>Your Earnings</h3>
      <p>For this trip, you will earn: <strong style="font-size: 1.3rem; color: #2e7d32;">${{driverEarningAmount}}</strong></p>
      <p>Payment will be processed according to your regular payment schedule after trip completion.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="footer">
      <h3>Need Assistance?</h3>
      <p>Contact dispatch if you have any questions about this reservation.</p>
      <a href="mailto:support@abyridellc.com">support@abyridellc.com</a>
      <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9;">
        Thank you for driving with AbyRide<br>
        <em>Safe travels!</em>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>